WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:14.980 align:middle line:90%


00:00:14.980 --> 00:00:16.520 align:middle line:84%
Hello, my delicious
co-creators.

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:17.650 align:middle line:90%
Lilous here.

00:00:17.650 --> 00:00:21.041 align:middle line:84%
I'm in Toulouse, South of
France with Michael Roads.

00:00:21.041 --> 00:00:22.480 align:middle line:84%
Hellos, Michael.
-Good morning, Lilou.

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:24.250 align:middle line:90%
It's lovely being here.

00:00:24.250 --> 00:00:28.710 align:middle line:84%
It's cold and brisk and you look
as if it's a hot summer day.

00:00:28.710 --> 00:00:30.390 align:middle line:84%
It is absolutely
gorgeous weather.

00:00:30.390 --> 00:00:32.079 align:middle line:90%
This man is from Australia.

00:00:32.079 --> 00:00:32.930 align:middle line:90%
It's gorgeous.

00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:34.494 align:middle line:84%
It's cloudy.
It's cold.

00:00:34.494 --> 00:00:35.580 align:middle line:90%
It's gorgeous.

00:00:35.580 --> 00:00:37.756 align:middle line:84%
But those clouds,
aren't they great?

00:00:37.756 --> 00:00:38.730 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, they're shining.

00:00:38.730 --> 00:00:39.950 align:middle line:84%
They're beaming
out, aren't they?

00:00:39.950 --> 00:00:40.650 align:middle line:90%
They are.

00:00:40.650 --> 00:00:42.785 align:middle line:90%
They're our sun.

00:00:42.785 --> 00:00:45.910 align:middle line:84%
When you're with nature, you
can create your own rules

00:00:45.910 --> 00:00:47.360 align:middle line:90%
to a certain extent.

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:51.430 align:middle line:84%
When I was about nine
years old, I used to go

00:00:51.430 --> 00:00:52.600 align:middle line:90%
and visit a friend of mine.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:56.560 align:middle line:84%
He had a great aunt
and she was in her 90s.

00:00:56.560 --> 00:00:59.710 align:middle line:84%
And she lived in a terraced
house and the back of the house

00:00:59.710 --> 00:01:01.860 align:middle line:90%
was a very small garden.

00:01:01.860 --> 00:01:05.670 align:middle line:84%
And it had about three
meter walls all around it.

00:01:05.670 --> 00:01:08.070 align:middle line:84%
And I at nine, knew
a lot about plants.

00:01:08.070 --> 00:01:10.800 align:middle line:84%
I had a collection
of about 200 or 300.

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:15.320 align:middle line:84%
And I would go in her garden
and everything was in flower.

00:01:15.320 --> 00:01:18.060 align:middle line:84%
And most of it was in pots,
but everything was in flower.

00:01:18.060 --> 00:01:19.220 align:middle line:90%
And I couldn't understand it.

00:01:19.220 --> 00:01:23.250 align:middle line:84%
Because generally
speaking, for most plants,

00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:25.550 align:middle line:90%
flowers are the result of sun.

00:01:25.550 --> 00:01:27.410 align:middle line:84%
There are many
specialist plants.

00:01:27.410 --> 00:01:30.330 align:middle line:84%
But generally, the sun is
what brings out the flower.

00:01:30.330 --> 00:01:32.660 align:middle line:84%
And in her garden, the sun
hardly ever got in there.

00:01:32.660 --> 00:01:35.500 align:middle line:84%
It was in there maybe, even
in the summer, only an hour

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:36.830 align:middle line:90%
or two or three at the most.

00:01:36.830 --> 00:01:39.240 align:middle line:84%
And yet, everything
was in flower.

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.830 align:middle line:90%
And I used to think about this.

00:01:40.830 --> 00:01:42.750 align:middle line:84%
How come these
things are in flower?

00:01:42.750 --> 00:01:44.090 align:middle line:90%
They shouldn't be.

00:01:44.090 --> 00:01:48.170 align:middle line:84%
And one day, I was watching
her and she stood there,

00:01:48.170 --> 00:01:50.030 align:middle line:90%
and she radiating love.

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:53.040 align:middle line:84%
And I realized, wow, she's
the sun in the garden.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:57.010 align:middle line:84%
Her love was the sun in that
little back yard garden.

00:01:57.010 --> 00:02:00.170 align:middle line:84%
And I never forgot
that, obviously.

00:02:00.170 --> 00:02:03.670 align:middle line:84%
Since then you really have
this love affair with nature,

00:02:03.670 --> 00:02:06.860 align:middle line:84%
and you have this is a
special bond with it.

00:02:06.860 --> 00:02:09.750 align:middle line:84%
And I find that this is
essential in our society right

00:02:09.750 --> 00:02:13.500 align:middle line:84%
now to go back to nature,
to connect with it,

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:16.760 align:middle line:84%
to see how beautiful it
is, how it is there for us.

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:22.260 align:middle line:84%
What is to you,
the role of nature?

00:02:22.260 --> 00:02:25.640 align:middle line:84%
Well, before we can
connect really with nature,

00:02:25.640 --> 00:02:27.360 align:middle line:84%
we have to connect
with ourselves.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:29.030 align:middle line:84%
Before we can
connect with nature,

00:02:29.030 --> 00:02:32.020 align:middle line:84%
we have to see that
there's no separation,

00:02:32.020 --> 00:02:34.670 align:middle line:84%
and that, if we
look from our eyes

00:02:34.670 --> 00:02:37.430 align:middle line:84%
over at those trees and
the plants around us,

00:02:37.430 --> 00:02:39.570 align:middle line:90%
we see the space between them.

00:02:39.570 --> 00:02:42.980 align:middle line:84%
So we believe that
we're separate.

00:02:42.980 --> 00:02:46.770 align:middle line:84%
And we live in a world with
the illusion of separation.

00:02:46.770 --> 00:02:51.600 align:middle line:84%
We have words like oneness,
but they're just words.

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:55.210 align:middle line:84%
Scientists talk about a
unified field of energy,

00:02:55.210 --> 00:02:57.370 align:middle line:90%
but they never experienced it.

00:02:57.370 --> 00:02:59.090 align:middle line:84%
So they have that
intellectually.

00:02:59.090 --> 00:03:03.300 align:middle line:84%
They tell us for instance of
the movement, of shall we say,

00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:06.670 align:middle line:84%
a bear in Canada affects
a movement of maybe

00:03:06.670 --> 00:03:08.780 align:middle line:90%
a kangaroo in Australia.

00:03:08.780 --> 00:03:12.340 align:middle line:84%
And that's very nice
as a scientific fact,

00:03:12.340 --> 00:03:14.640 align:middle line:84%
but to experience
that connection,

00:03:14.640 --> 00:03:18.410 align:middle line:84%
that unified field of energy,
is something very different.

00:03:18.410 --> 00:03:22.450 align:middle line:84%
And so when you're
connecting with nature,

00:03:22.450 --> 00:03:23.760 align:middle line:84%
the first thing
you have to do is

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:25.780 align:middle line:84%
realize that, shall
we say a tree,

00:03:25.780 --> 00:03:28.510 align:middle line:90%
that is a field of energy.

00:03:28.510 --> 00:03:30.670 align:middle line:90%
And you are a field of energy.

00:03:30.670 --> 00:03:35.520 align:middle line:84%
And the fields of
energy are not separate.

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:37.400 align:middle line:84%
And so if, as a
field of energy, you

00:03:37.400 --> 00:03:40.690 align:middle line:84%
go to a tree that is
a field of energy,

00:03:40.690 --> 00:03:44.090 align:middle line:84%
you connect in a
place of oneness.

00:03:44.090 --> 00:03:48.130 align:middle line:84%
So it's not a person
communicating with a tree.

00:03:48.130 --> 00:03:49.980 align:middle line:84%
There's nothing
like that at all.

00:03:49.980 --> 00:03:53.200 align:middle line:84%
There is energy
exchanging energy.

00:03:53.200 --> 00:03:55.000 align:middle line:90%
Now, all energy is information.

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.900 align:middle line:90%
All information is energy.

00:03:56.900 --> 00:03:59.100 align:middle line:84%
And so when you
approach a tree, you

00:03:59.100 --> 00:04:02.292 align:middle line:84%
are radiating information to
that tree whether you know it

00:04:02.292 --> 00:04:03.080 align:middle line:90%
or not.

00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:05.780 align:middle line:84%
People go and talk to the
tree and ask it questions.

00:04:05.780 --> 00:04:07.290 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing to ask it.

00:04:07.290 --> 00:04:11.630 align:middle line:84%
It's already-- it's
like, nature doesn't

00:04:11.630 --> 00:04:13.190 align:middle line:90%
have to learn to talk with us.

00:04:13.190 --> 00:04:15.470 align:middle line:90%
We have to learn to listen.

00:04:15.470 --> 00:04:16.779 align:middle line:84%
And so the first
thing you've got

00:04:16.779 --> 00:04:20.140 align:middle line:84%
to do if you're going to
really communicate with a tree

00:04:20.140 --> 00:04:24.330 align:middle line:84%
is get past this
communication barrier.

00:04:24.330 --> 00:04:26.560 align:middle line:90%
And you do that by listening.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:29.600 align:middle line:90%
So a tree occupies a moment.

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.510 align:middle line:90%
We also occupy the moment.

00:04:31.510 --> 00:04:33.050 align:middle line:90%
But we think.

00:04:33.050 --> 00:04:35.660 align:middle line:84%
And thinking takes
you out of the moment.

00:04:35.660 --> 00:04:38.460 align:middle line:84%
You cannot think your
way into the moment.

00:04:38.460 --> 00:04:41.130 align:middle line:84%
So you think about that
when you're not thinking.

00:04:41.130 --> 00:04:46.100 align:middle line:84%
You cannot think your
way into the moment.

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:50.950 align:middle line:84%
And people are thinking
like 60,000 thoughts a day,

00:04:50.950 --> 00:04:54.200 align:middle line:84%
probably about 80% of
them, negative thoughts.

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:55.430 align:middle line:90%
Trees are not doing that.

00:04:55.430 --> 00:04:56.310 align:middle line:90%
There's no thinking.

00:04:56.310 --> 00:04:58.560 align:middle line:84%
There's no negative
thoughts going on.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:03.660 align:middle line:84%
And so people get
disconnected from each other.

00:05:03.660 --> 00:05:05.660 align:middle line:90%
And disconnected is a good word.

00:05:05.660 --> 00:05:08.800 align:middle line:84%
People are disconnected
from life, from the self,

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:10.430 align:middle line:90%
and therefore from nature.

00:05:10.430 --> 00:05:11.920 align:middle line:90%
But nature is connected.

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:15.240 align:middle line:84%
Everything in nature is
connected in that unified field

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:16.480 align:middle line:90%
of energy.

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:18.580 align:middle line:84%
It's not an
intellectual connection.

00:05:18.580 --> 00:05:21.430 align:middle line:84%
And we always think that this
has got to be intellectual.

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:25.580 align:middle line:84%
So nature has no intellect
but it has intelligence.

00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:28.200 align:middle line:84%
It has consciousness,
despite what

00:05:28.200 --> 00:05:30.150 align:middle line:90%
science says to the country.

00:05:30.150 --> 00:05:34.680 align:middle line:84%
So a tree doesn't
grow just a tree.

00:05:34.680 --> 00:05:38.460 align:middle line:84%
The tree is the
physical reflection

00:05:38.460 --> 00:05:41.930 align:middle line:90%
and a metaphysical mirror.

00:05:41.930 --> 00:05:42.800 align:middle line:90%
I'll rephrase that.

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:45.300 align:middle line:84%
It's the physical
reflection from the mirror

00:05:45.300 --> 00:05:47.870 align:middle line:90%
of a greater reality.

00:05:47.870 --> 00:05:49.315 align:middle line:84%
Where the physical
tree is, there

00:05:49.315 --> 00:05:51.900 align:middle line:84%
is also a metaphysical
tree, which

00:05:51.900 --> 00:05:53.700 align:middle line:90%
means beyond the physical.

00:05:53.700 --> 00:05:56.870 align:middle line:84%
And that's where the
communication takes place.

00:05:56.870 --> 00:06:01.060 align:middle line:84%
So you mean there is this aura
field around the tree itself

00:06:01.060 --> 00:06:02.700 align:middle line:84%
and that's where
it happens like us?

00:06:02.700 --> 00:06:04.320 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes you can
see that aura field

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:07.090 align:middle line:84%
but the metaphysical tree
is far more than that.

00:06:07.090 --> 00:06:09.260 align:middle line:84%
It's much greater
than the physical.

00:06:09.260 --> 00:06:11.050 align:middle line:90%
It's far more beautiful.

00:06:11.050 --> 00:06:15.600 align:middle line:84%
It has many colors and it's
just a complete field of energy,

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.430 align:middle line:90%
as is the physical tree.

00:06:17.430 --> 00:06:20.420 align:middle line:84%
But the field of energy
from which it expresses,

00:06:20.420 --> 00:06:22.810 align:middle line:84%
I have seen trees
cut down physically

00:06:22.810 --> 00:06:26.520 align:middle line:84%
and I've seen the metaphysical
trees still standing there.

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:29.030 align:middle line:84%
And you're not about
to cut that down.

00:06:29.030 --> 00:06:30.470 align:middle line:90%
And it's the same with us.

00:06:30.470 --> 00:06:33.830 align:middle line:84%
You lose your physical body,
but you're still alive,

00:06:33.830 --> 00:06:34.820 align:middle line:90%
and you're still a being.

00:06:34.820 --> 00:06:36.220 align:middle line:90%
You're still a person.

00:06:36.220 --> 00:06:38.530 align:middle line:84%
But you no longer
have a physical body.

00:06:38.530 --> 00:06:40.520 align:middle line:90%
It's exactly the same in nature.

00:06:40.520 --> 00:06:44.270 align:middle line:84%
So in other words,
we are immortal.

00:06:44.270 --> 00:06:45.570 align:middle line:90%
Which is nice.

00:06:45.570 --> 00:06:48.200 align:middle line:90%
It sort of lasts a long time.

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:52.070 align:middle line:84%
And so every human
being is immortal,

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:54.940 align:middle line:84%
no human being is born
and no human being dies.

00:06:54.940 --> 00:06:56.510 align:middle line:90%
It's the same in nature.

00:06:56.510 --> 00:06:57.420 align:middle line:90%
Nothing is born.

00:06:57.420 --> 00:06:58.290 align:middle line:90%
Nothing dies.

00:06:58.290 --> 00:07:02.460 align:middle line:84%
But in nature, the consciousness
of nature knows this.

00:07:02.460 --> 00:07:05.770 align:middle line:84%
So nature has no
relationship with death.

00:07:05.770 --> 00:07:08.670 align:middle line:84%
Because it doesn't exist
in its reality frame.

00:07:08.670 --> 00:07:11.650 align:middle line:84%
We have a relationship with
death because we fear it.

00:07:11.650 --> 00:07:13.610 align:middle line:84%
And so we've created
something fearful.

00:07:13.610 --> 00:07:15.300 align:middle line:90%
But there is no such thing.

00:07:15.300 --> 00:07:16.900 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't exist.

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:20.230 align:middle line:84%
So you sit beneath a tree and
you allow your field of energy

00:07:20.230 --> 00:07:22.460 align:middle line:90%
to connect.

00:07:22.460 --> 00:07:25.800 align:middle line:84%
Is that at this point, do we
have to raise our own frequency

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:27.210 align:middle line:90%
also to be there?

00:07:27.210 --> 00:07:28.790 align:middle line:84%
Some people say that,
so I was wondering.

00:07:28.790 --> 00:07:30.210 align:middle line:90%
What an interesting question.

00:07:30.210 --> 00:07:32.250 align:middle line:84%
Many people couldn't
do this because they

00:07:32.250 --> 00:07:34.590 align:middle line:90%
would sit there and think.

00:07:34.590 --> 00:07:37.520 align:middle line:84%
But if you're sitting there
and you're not thinking,

00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:40.640 align:middle line:84%
and you're just a silent
as you can be but certainly

00:07:40.640 --> 00:07:42.180 align:middle line:90%
your thoughts are raised.

00:07:42.180 --> 00:07:43.060 align:middle line:90%
If you have raised.

00:07:43.060 --> 00:07:46.990 align:middle line:84%
So, yes, you're thinking love
and respect and appreciation,

00:07:46.990 --> 00:07:47.880 align:middle line:90%
and things like that.

00:07:47.880 --> 00:07:49.170 align:middle line:84%
That definitely
lifts your energy.

00:07:49.170 --> 00:07:50.600 align:middle line:90%
No question.

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:52.470 align:middle line:84%
This is what the
transition's all about,

00:07:52.470 --> 00:07:54.510 align:middle line:90%
this energetic shift.

00:07:54.510 --> 00:07:57.160 align:middle line:84%
And the dimensional
shift, it's pure energy,

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:58.750 align:middle line:90%
pure consciousness.

00:07:58.750 --> 00:08:01.810 align:middle line:84%
Anyway and so you
listen, you listen.

00:08:01.810 --> 00:08:04.700 align:middle line:84%
Now I used to go
down by the river.

00:08:04.700 --> 00:08:06.030 align:middle line:90%
And I had an old bridge board.

00:08:06.030 --> 00:08:08.130 align:middle line:90%
And I would sit there each day.

00:08:08.130 --> 00:08:10.950 align:middle line:84%
And I would spend an hour or
two listening to the river.

00:08:10.950 --> 00:08:13.920 align:middle line:84%
And at first all I heard
was the physical river.

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:16.550 align:middle line:84%
It took me six
years of going down

00:08:16.550 --> 00:08:18.240 align:middle line:90%
to learn to listen to nature.

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:20.300 align:middle line:90%
I used to just sit and listen.

00:08:20.300 --> 00:08:23.780 align:middle line:84%
And one time I was down
there and the river

00:08:23.780 --> 00:08:26.610 align:middle line:90%
said, do you see me as new?

00:08:26.610 --> 00:08:28.360 align:middle line:90%
And I knew I didn't.

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:30.990 align:middle line:84%
And so I had to
learn to see newness.

00:08:30.990 --> 00:08:33.850 align:middle line:84%
And what I learned was,
only the newness of me

00:08:33.850 --> 00:08:36.950 align:middle line:84%
could see the newness of life
and the newness of a river.

00:08:36.950 --> 00:08:40.059 align:middle line:84%
But when I learned how
to finally do that,

00:08:40.059 --> 00:08:42.979 align:middle line:84%
it's as though the river stopped
flowing on the outside of me

00:08:42.979 --> 00:08:44.400 align:middle line:90%
and flowed through me.

00:08:44.400 --> 00:08:47.240 align:middle line:84%
Because I was-- and I don't
mean the physical mean.

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:50.620 align:middle line:84%
I don't like rivers flowing
from the physical me.

00:08:50.620 --> 00:08:52.370 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't help
with your breathing.

00:08:52.370 --> 00:08:54.520 align:middle line:84%
Don't even like rain
flowing through me.

00:08:54.520 --> 00:08:59.750 align:middle line:84%
So what I'm saying is,
and so the field of energy

00:08:59.750 --> 00:09:01.900 align:middle line:84%
allows nature to
move through it.

00:09:01.900 --> 00:09:05.800 align:middle line:84%
And so we see ourselves walking
in a forest through nature.

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:09.350 align:middle line:84%
But when you move into
yourself as a field of energy,

00:09:09.350 --> 00:09:11.580 align:middle line:84%
you can sit in
the forest and let

00:09:11.580 --> 00:09:14.140 align:middle line:90%
the forest move through you.

00:09:14.140 --> 00:09:16.480 align:middle line:84%
But people don't
do that, especially

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:17.500 align:middle line:90%
when they get my age.

00:09:17.500 --> 00:09:19.830 align:middle line:84%
They say, oh, I walked
25 kilometers a day

00:09:19.830 --> 00:09:21.670 align:middle line:90%
through such and such forest.

00:09:21.670 --> 00:09:23.300 align:middle line:90%
Another one, oh, I did 30 today.

00:09:23.300 --> 00:09:24.890 align:middle line:90%
Isn't that good.

00:09:24.890 --> 00:09:27.960 align:middle line:84%
And I was talking to a group of
these ones and I said to them,

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:31.140 align:middle line:84%
did anybody ever consider doing
like 100 meters of actually

00:09:31.140 --> 00:09:33.750 align:middle line:90%
seeing what you walk past?

00:09:33.750 --> 00:09:39.020 align:middle line:84%
Having a loop, and looking at
the holes of trap door spiders

00:09:39.020 --> 00:09:42.560 align:middle line:84%
and seeing how many spider
holes on little trap doors

00:09:42.560 --> 00:09:45.800 align:middle line:84%
there are just along
five meters of ground.

00:09:45.800 --> 00:09:47.310 align:middle line:84%
And of course they
didn't do that.

00:09:47.310 --> 00:09:51.350 align:middle line:84%
And they didn't receive the
comment very well either.

