00:19:29.990 --> 00:19:33.270 align:middle line:84%
attacks and going through myself
through this is huge money

00:19:33.270 --> 00:19:34.870 align:middle line:90%
and crisis challenge.

00:19:34.870 --> 00:19:37.460 align:middle line:84%
And I feel a lot of people are
going through that right now.

00:19:37.460 --> 00:19:39.250 align:middle line:84%
And when we have those
huge panic attacks

00:19:39.250 --> 00:19:40.680 align:middle line:84%
and it feels like
in that moment,

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:43.320 align:middle line:84%
there was only nature
that could do something.

00:19:43.320 --> 00:19:45.620 align:middle line:84%
There was only--
not do something,

00:19:45.620 --> 00:19:47.600 align:middle line:84%
but that's where I was
coming from at the time.

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:50.630 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, from
that suffering place,

00:19:50.630 --> 00:19:54.490 align:middle line:84%
there is this opening that
was created in the heart.

00:19:54.490 --> 00:19:57.950 align:middle line:84%
And it's like, sometimes
nature absorbs also and helps

00:19:57.950 --> 00:19:59.670 align:middle line:84%
us to go through
those hard moments

00:19:59.670 --> 00:20:01.870 align:middle line:90%
and can lift us up, literally.

00:20:01.870 --> 00:20:10.110 align:middle line:84%
I mean to me, they're are huge
key to huge challenging times

00:20:10.110 --> 00:20:12.191 align:middle line:84%
that the world is going
through right now.

00:20:12.191 --> 00:20:12.890 align:middle line:90%
I agree.

00:20:12.890 --> 00:20:14.790 align:middle line:84%
I'm not sure whether
you're trying

00:20:14.790 --> 00:20:17.170 align:middle line:84%
to keep me talking about
nature or whether you

00:20:17.170 --> 00:20:18.560 align:middle line:90%
actually believe what you said.

00:20:18.560 --> 00:20:21.940 align:middle line:84%
I don't believe nature
took you out of your panic.

00:20:21.940 --> 00:20:25.180 align:middle line:90%
I think you grew through it.

00:20:25.180 --> 00:20:27.910 align:middle line:84%
And you shifted your
focus, and began

00:20:27.910 --> 00:20:30.570 align:middle line:84%
to find your security
more in your heart

00:20:30.570 --> 00:20:32.113 align:middle line:90%
than in everything around you.

00:20:32.113 --> 00:20:34.450 align:middle line:84%
-But isn't that the whole key?
-Exactly.

00:20:34.450 --> 00:20:36.270 align:middle line:84%
And nature can
help that for sure.

00:20:36.270 --> 00:20:38.200 align:middle line:84%
But as I said,
nobody's listening.

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:40.230 align:middle line:84%
But it's lovely to
connect with nature.

00:20:40.230 --> 00:20:42.790 align:middle line:84%
I remember also,
I remember I only

00:20:42.790 --> 00:20:44.950 align:middle line:90%
ever have one panic attack.

00:20:44.950 --> 00:20:47.670 align:middle line:90%
And we'd started a community.

00:20:47.670 --> 00:20:50.970 align:middle line:84%
I started a spiritual
community in which I lived in,

00:20:50.970 --> 00:20:53.720 align:middle line:84%
which was really creating
in the classroom for myself.

00:20:53.720 --> 00:20:55.360 align:middle line:84%
But there's a lot of
other people in there.

00:20:55.360 --> 00:20:57.300 align:middle line:84%
And I think I said yesterday
I didn't like them.

00:20:57.300 --> 00:20:58.560 align:middle line:90%
They didn't like me.

00:20:58.560 --> 00:21:00.390 align:middle line:84%
And then I found
I didn't like me.

00:21:00.390 --> 00:21:02.380 align:middle line:90%
But I ran out of money.

00:21:02.380 --> 00:21:05.100 align:middle line:84%
And I was sitting on the
bed one day in our caravan

00:21:05.100 --> 00:21:08.310 align:middle line:84%
which Americans call a
trailer, but a caravan.

00:21:08.310 --> 00:21:10.460 align:middle line:84%
And I was thinking,
my god, you know,

00:21:10.460 --> 00:21:14.640 align:middle line:84%
I have four children and
a wife and I have $200.

00:21:14.640 --> 00:21:17.450 align:middle line:84%
That's all I have,
absolutely nothing else.

00:21:17.450 --> 00:21:19.980 align:middle line:84%
And I was really getting
very, very anxious

00:21:19.980 --> 00:21:20.910 align:middle line:90%
and sort of sweating.

00:21:20.910 --> 00:21:22.170 align:middle line:90%
And I thought this is terrible.

00:21:22.170 --> 00:21:25.070 align:middle line:84%
And the door opened and
my late wife came in.

00:21:25.070 --> 00:21:28.000 align:middle line:84%
And she said to me, do you
know how much money we've got?

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:30.740 align:middle line:90%
And foolishly, I said, no.

00:21:30.740 --> 00:21:33.870 align:middle line:90%
And she said, $4.

00:21:33.870 --> 00:21:35.800 align:middle line:84%
And she walked down
and shut the door.

00:21:35.800 --> 00:21:39.710 align:middle line:84%
She said she didn't slam it,
but she shut it very forcefully.

00:21:39.710 --> 00:21:43.560 align:middle line:84%
And do you know, I was
so humiliated, in my 40s.

00:21:43.560 --> 00:21:47.780 align:middle line:84%
I was so humiliated, so ashamed
of myself and so terrified

00:21:47.780 --> 00:21:50.780 align:middle line:84%
by this, I was sitting on
the bed and passed out.

00:21:50.780 --> 00:21:52.330 align:middle line:90%
I just passed out.

00:21:52.330 --> 00:21:54.850 align:middle line:84%
I realized that prior
to her coming in,

00:21:54.850 --> 00:21:57.820 align:middle line:84%
I'd only been practicing
for a panic attack.

00:21:57.820 --> 00:21:59.600 align:middle line:90%
So then I had a real one.

00:21:59.600 --> 00:22:01.830 align:middle line:84%
And when I came around,
you know what happened?

00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:02.530 align:middle line:90%
Nothing.

00:22:02.530 --> 00:22:04.630 align:middle line:90%
I still only had $4.

00:22:04.630 --> 00:22:06.690 align:middle line:84%
But I realized I
could never ever

00:22:06.690 --> 00:22:08.960 align:middle line:90%
be more frightened than that.

00:22:08.960 --> 00:22:11.460 align:middle line:84%
And having literally
passed out from fear,

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:13.480 align:middle line:84%
it's as though I looked
at fear and thought,

00:22:13.480 --> 00:22:16.310 align:middle line:84%
God, you're a bit of a
toothless tiger, aren't you?

00:22:16.310 --> 00:22:17.931 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's so
I've only got $4.

00:22:17.931 --> 00:22:19.310 align:middle line:84%
So what?
We can manage.

00:22:19.310 --> 00:22:20.800 align:middle line:90%
We'll get through this.

00:22:20.800 --> 00:22:24.510 align:middle line:84%
And in that moment, my
whole attitude changed.

00:22:24.510 --> 00:22:25.862 align:middle line:90%
And this is what abundance is.

00:22:25.862 --> 00:22:26.880 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:30.240 align:middle line:84%
Abundance is a shift
in consciousness.

00:22:30.240 --> 00:22:32.720 align:middle line:84%
It's like I mentioned, every
time we look in a window

00:22:32.720 --> 00:22:35.520 align:middle line:84%
and say, I can't
afford, we feed poverty.

00:22:35.520 --> 00:22:38.110 align:middle line:84%
But every time-- and this
is where nature comes in,

00:22:38.110 --> 00:22:40.320 align:middle line:84%
when you look at nature
and you realize that it

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:42.370 align:middle line:90%
doesn't go out window shopping.

00:22:42.370 --> 00:22:45.280 align:middle line:84%
Nature doesn't go
out looking for food.

00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:48.620 align:middle line:84%
Squirrels and many of the
animals go looking for food.

00:22:48.620 --> 00:22:52.020 align:middle line:84%
But so much of nature
stands passively there

00:22:52.020 --> 00:22:54.370 align:middle line:90%
and food comes to it.

00:22:54.370 --> 00:22:59.510 align:middle line:84%
A lot of the predators, ambush
predators, food comes to it.

00:22:59.510 --> 00:23:00.880 align:middle line:90%
Some of them hunt.

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:05.300 align:middle line:84%
But nature doesn't ever look a
life-- nothing in nature looks

00:23:05.300 --> 00:23:07.130 align:middle line:90%
at life as lack.

00:23:07.130 --> 00:23:10.390 align:middle line:90%
We have a big focus on lack.

00:23:10.390 --> 00:23:12.890 align:middle line:84%
We don't have a
focus on abundance.

00:23:12.890 --> 00:23:14.780 align:middle line:84%
And so when you
focus on abundance

00:23:14.780 --> 00:23:18.310 align:middle line:84%
and you think from abundance,
and you feel from abundance,

00:23:18.310 --> 00:23:19.390 align:middle line:90%
and that's really important.

00:23:19.390 --> 00:23:20.790 align:middle line:90%
You feel abundance.

00:23:20.790 --> 00:23:23.040 align:middle line:84%
Then, that moves into
your consciousness.

00:23:23.040 --> 00:23:27.060 align:middle line:84%
But I suspect sometimes we
need to reach that point

00:23:27.060 --> 00:23:31.400 align:middle line:84%
issue of terror of not having
enough to realize finally,

00:23:31.400 --> 00:23:32.610 align:middle line:90%
I created this.

00:23:32.610 --> 00:23:34.150 align:middle line:84%
I don't have enough
because I always

00:23:34.150 --> 00:23:35.900 align:middle line:90%
focus on not having enough.

00:23:35.900 --> 00:23:39.460 align:middle line:84%
It feels to me like the
certain world needs to collapse.

00:23:39.460 --> 00:23:43.100 align:middle line:84%
And then there is pain and
suffering but our own world.

00:23:43.100 --> 00:23:46.970 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, there
is this huge fear and panic.

00:23:46.970 --> 00:23:48.840 align:middle line:90%
And how am I going to do this?

00:23:48.840 --> 00:23:52.880 align:middle line:84%
And there's suffering so deep,
that you just have to-- I mean

00:23:52.880 --> 00:23:54.620 align:middle line:84%
I remember myself
being on my knees

00:23:54.620 --> 00:23:56.490 align:middle line:84%
and praying and asking
for another answer.

00:23:56.490 --> 00:23:58.880 align:middle line:84%
I've never found myself
in the situation before.

00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:00.670 align:middle line:84%
And it was so much--
it was just unbearable.

00:24:00.670 --> 00:24:04.040 align:middle line:84%
And at some point it's like,
there is this crossover.

00:24:04.040 --> 00:24:06.390 align:middle line:84%
There is this little-- how
would you call this step

00:24:06.390 --> 00:24:09.650 align:middle line:84%
from the suffering and
this pain and this locked

00:24:09.650 --> 00:24:14.980 align:middle line:84%
in world to one that is
expanded and unites everything?

00:24:14.980 --> 00:24:17.230 align:middle line:90%
That's an interesting question.

00:24:17.230 --> 00:24:19.940 align:middle line:84%
I don't know there is
a name for that state,

00:24:19.940 --> 00:24:22.050 align:middle line:84%
but there is a
shifting consciousness.

00:24:22.050 --> 00:24:25.250 align:middle line:84%
And I think we have to get to
that desperate point, which

00:24:25.250 --> 00:24:26.810 align:middle line:90%
everybody avoids.

00:24:26.810 --> 00:24:31.130 align:middle line:84%
But then, that place
is a knife edge.

00:24:31.130 --> 00:24:34.080 align:middle line:90%
And one edge one way is suicide.

00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:37.500 align:middle line:84%
And the other way is back
in to life with more power

00:24:37.500 --> 00:24:38.950 align:middle line:90%
than you've ever had.

00:24:38.950 --> 00:24:41.760 align:middle line:84%
Unfortunately, the suicide
rates in every country

00:24:41.760 --> 00:24:44.290 align:middle line:84%
are escalating at
an incredible speed.

00:24:44.290 --> 00:24:48.480 align:middle line:84%
And the people who
suddenly find life

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:54.010 align:middle line:84%
in that incredible moment,
which we create, we manufacture.

00:24:54.010 --> 00:24:56.260 align:middle line:84%
But it's as though,
really, energy,

00:24:56.260 --> 00:24:58.395 align:middle line:90%
where you focus energy flows.

00:24:58.395 --> 00:25:02.290 align:middle line:84%
And when you're on that
razor edge, of everything's

00:25:02.290 --> 00:25:03.960 align:middle line:90%
gone wrong, you're broke.

00:25:03.960 --> 00:25:06.480 align:middle line:90%
You're frightened.

00:25:06.480 --> 00:25:08.170 align:middle line:84%
I think one of the
clues is when you

00:25:08.170 --> 00:25:11.880 align:middle line:84%
can actually admit that to
yourself, when you can say,

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:13.010 align:middle line:90%
I have no money.

00:25:13.010 --> 00:25:14.640 align:middle line:90%
I'm terrified.

00:25:14.640 --> 00:25:15.890 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what to do.

00:25:15.890 --> 00:25:16.840 align:middle line:90%
I don't know where to go.

00:25:16.840 --> 00:25:18.700 align:middle line:90%
I don't know how to handle this.

00:25:18.700 --> 00:25:22.910 align:middle line:84%
And you can honestly accept
and acknowledge all the fears,

00:25:22.910 --> 00:25:24.990 align:middle line:84%
and then suddenly when
you've said them all,

00:25:24.990 --> 00:25:27.240 align:middle line:90%
it doesn't quite seem so bad.

00:25:27.240 --> 00:25:30.780 align:middle line:84%
I mean when I was a
farmer in Tasmania,

00:25:30.780 --> 00:25:35.160 align:middle line:84%
we went through the worst decade
of farming in the 20th century.

00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:38.010 align:middle line:84%
We arrived, emigrated, just
for the beginning of it,

00:25:38.010 --> 00:25:39.700 align:middle line:90%
like as if I needed that.

00:25:39.700 --> 00:25:41.350 align:middle line:90%
But I did need that.

00:25:41.350 --> 00:25:43.140 align:middle line:90%
I got there in perfect timing.

00:25:43.140 --> 00:25:44.710 align:middle line:90%
We went into drought.

00:25:44.710 --> 00:25:46.900 align:middle line:84%
First, we had a
caterpillar plague.

00:25:46.900 --> 00:25:48.040 align:middle line:90%
I mean, you can't imagine it.

00:25:48.040 --> 00:25:50.430 align:middle line:84%
Locusts, you know
what they're like.

00:25:50.430 --> 00:25:51.930 align:middle line:84%
Locusts, they're
big grasshoppers,

00:25:51.930 --> 00:25:53.350 align:middle line:90%
flying grasshoppers.

00:25:53.350 --> 00:25:55.720 align:middle line:84%
OK, a locust plague
strips everything.

00:25:55.720 --> 00:25:58.830 align:middle line:84%
Well, so does a caterpillar
plague, except they don't fly.

00:25:58.830 --> 00:26:01.180 align:middle line:90%
They crawl through your house.

00:26:01.180 --> 00:26:03.500 align:middle line:84%
You have to grease band
the house to keep them out.

00:26:03.500 --> 00:26:04.570 align:middle line:90%
You can't imagine.

00:26:04.570 --> 00:26:07.210 align:middle line:84%
You're hens, chickens,
they eat the caterpillars

00:26:07.210 --> 00:26:08.850 align:middle line:90%
and lay green eggs.

00:26:08.850 --> 00:26:10.300 align:middle line:90%
You can't eat the eggs.

00:26:10.300 --> 00:26:13.290 align:middle line:84%
And so, they go across your
farm and they strip it.

00:26:13.290 --> 00:26:14.720 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing left.

00:26:14.720 --> 00:26:16.090 align:middle line:90%
Everything's gone that's green.

00:26:16.090 --> 00:26:17.150 align:middle line:90%
It's brown.

00:26:17.150 --> 00:26:20.170 align:middle line:90%
And the cows were dying.

00:26:20.170 --> 00:26:21.925 align:middle line:90%
And then we went into drought.

00:26:21.925 --> 00:26:25.670 align:middle line:84%
And the drought went
on year after year.

00:26:25.670 --> 00:26:26.690 align:middle line:90%
That lasted three years.

00:26:26.690 --> 00:26:30.720 align:middle line:84%
Then we went into an economic
recession in agriculture.

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:32.840 align:middle line:84%
In the cities,
everything was booming.

00:26:32.840 --> 00:26:35.690 align:middle line:84%
In agricultural,
prices of [INAUDIBLE]

00:26:35.690 --> 00:26:40.820 align:middle line:90%
went from $350 to $5.

00:26:40.820 --> 00:26:43.460 align:middle line:84%
And farmers were
suiciding everywhere.

00:26:43.460 --> 00:26:46.570 align:middle line:90%
And one day, we were desperate.

00:26:46.570 --> 00:26:48.600 align:middle line:84%
This was my late wife
and I, we were desperate.

00:26:48.600 --> 00:26:51.950 align:middle line:84%
And so we went up onto the
highest hills of our farm

00:26:51.950 --> 00:26:53.920 align:middle line:90%
and we said, what have we got?

00:26:53.920 --> 00:26:55.820 align:middle line:90%
We've got four lovely children.

00:26:55.820 --> 00:26:57.010 align:middle line:90%
We've got each other.

00:26:57.010 --> 00:26:57.790 align:middle line:90%
We've got love.

00:26:57.790 --> 00:26:59.430 align:middle line:84%
We've got a beautiful
farm, even if we

00:26:59.430 --> 00:27:01.050 align:middle line:90%
don't particularly own it.

00:27:01.050 --> 00:27:02.380 align:middle line:90%
We've got a lovely environment.

00:27:02.380 --> 00:27:04.670 align:middle line:84%
We've got the glorious
mountain up there.

00:27:04.670 --> 00:27:07.540 align:middle line:84%
And we went through all
the things that we've got.

00:27:07.540 --> 00:27:10.240 align:middle line:84%
Then we said, so
what don't we have?

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:11.170 align:middle line:90%
Money.

00:27:11.170 --> 00:27:13.430 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, changed
the whole perspective.

00:27:13.430 --> 00:27:15.860 align:middle line:84%
There was a great mountain
of what we did have

00:27:15.860 --> 00:27:17.820 align:middle line:90%
and one thing that was missing.

00:27:17.820 --> 00:27:19.810 align:middle line:84%
And what did we focus
on all the time?

00:27:19.810 --> 00:27:21.180 align:middle line:90%
Lack of money.

00:27:21.180 --> 00:27:23.360 align:middle line:90%
What an illusion.

00:27:23.360 --> 00:27:26.830 align:middle line:84%
Well, it was a truth and
yet it is an illusion.

00:27:26.830 --> 00:27:30.980 align:middle line:84%
Because we focus on lack and
where you focus, energy flows.

00:27:30.980 --> 00:27:32.190 align:middle line:90%
And so it could never break.

00:27:32.190 --> 00:27:34.790 align:middle line:84%
So we began to focus
on what we had.

00:27:34.790 --> 00:27:37.940 align:middle line:84%
We began to focus on the
muchness of our life,

00:27:37.940 --> 00:27:39.760 align:middle line:84%
the abundance in
our life, and that

00:27:39.760 --> 00:27:41.320 align:middle line:90%
began to change everything.

00:27:41.320 --> 00:27:44.040 align:middle line:84%
And gradually, it all got
better and better and better.

00:27:44.040 --> 00:27:47.770 align:middle line:84%
And it wasn't just because that
the situation farming didn't

00:27:47.770 --> 00:27:49.690 align:middle line:84%
improve for a long
time, but it's

00:27:49.690 --> 00:27:51.980 align:middle line:90%
because our focus had shifted.

00:27:51.980 --> 00:27:54.750 align:middle line:84%
And one of the great
principles to remember in life

00:27:54.750 --> 00:27:57.140 align:middle line:84%
is, where you
focus, energy flows.

00:27:57.140 --> 00:27:59.320 align:middle line:84%
And the energy is
your own energy.

00:27:59.320 --> 00:28:01.620 align:middle line:84%
And it's your life
and it's your energy.

00:28:01.620 --> 00:28:03.700 align:middle line:84%
But I hear that you
also really let it

00:28:03.700 --> 00:28:05.810 align:middle line:84%
in, like through
gratitude, you were

00:28:05.810 --> 00:28:07.420 align:middle line:90%
able to open up the hearts.

00:28:07.420 --> 00:28:10.540 align:middle line:84%
And I feel like the abundance,
the hearts, and our love,

00:28:10.540 --> 00:28:12.060 align:middle line:90%
all that is connected.

00:28:12.060 --> 00:28:15.770 align:middle line:84%
And once you start to let
it in, and then let fear go,

00:28:15.770 --> 00:28:18.180 align:middle line:84%
there's this part
that starts inside

00:28:18.180 --> 00:28:20.480 align:middle line:84%
and it keeps on
growing from there.

00:28:20.480 --> 00:28:22.610 align:middle line:90%
But we have to let it in now.

00:28:22.610 --> 00:28:24.840 align:middle line:90%
This is the big thing.

00:28:24.840 --> 00:28:27.660 align:middle line:84%
The time we're in now, not only
is it easier to let in, I mean,

00:28:27.660 --> 00:28:30.440 align:middle line:84%
it's absolutely imperative
to let it in now,

00:28:30.440 --> 00:28:35.490 align:middle line:84%
to open, to open to
life, to open to love,

00:28:35.490 --> 00:28:38.410 align:middle line:90%
to open to gratitude, to focus.

00:28:38.410 --> 00:28:41.160 align:middle line:84%
We don't have to stop
thinking, to open

