00:39:56.010 --> 00:39:58.510 align:middle line:84%
I watch them moving, and
I watch their energy,

00:39:58.510 --> 00:39:59.840 align:middle line:90%
their fields of energy.

00:39:59.840 --> 00:40:01.950 align:middle line:90%
And fields of energy cluster.

00:40:01.950 --> 00:40:04.300 align:middle line:84%
If your body's sick and
they take a blood sample,

00:40:04.300 --> 00:40:06.620 align:middle line:84%
they look to see if the
platelets of your blood

00:40:06.620 --> 00:40:09.610 align:middle line:90%
stack or stick or cluster.

00:40:09.610 --> 00:40:11.280 align:middle line:84%
And if you're
sick, they cluster.

00:40:11.280 --> 00:40:13.490 align:middle line:84%
You look at a city,
people cluster.

00:40:13.490 --> 00:40:16.180 align:middle line:84%
Anger finds its
own energy and they

00:40:16.180 --> 00:40:18.280 align:middle line:84%
walk among each
other in clusters,

00:40:18.280 --> 00:40:19.760 align:middle line:90%
and they never even know it.

00:40:19.760 --> 00:40:27.950 align:middle line:84%
Boredom, you know, fear,
wanting, they all grow cluster.

00:40:27.950 --> 00:40:30.010 align:middle line:90%
They cluster in the restaurants.

00:40:30.010 --> 00:40:31.300 align:middle line:90%
They cluster walking around.

00:40:31.300 --> 00:40:33.120 align:middle line:84%
They cluster in
shopping centers.

00:40:33.120 --> 00:40:35.090 align:middle line:84%
They leave one cluster
and join another.

00:40:35.090 --> 00:40:35.970 align:middle line:90%
It's scary.

00:40:35.970 --> 00:40:37.590 align:middle line:84%
Because none of them
know they're doing it.

00:40:37.590 --> 00:40:41.680 align:middle line:84%
But there was one person-- and I
mean, there are many in a city,

00:40:41.680 --> 00:40:44.840 align:middle line:84%
but there's one type of
person who does not cluster.

00:40:44.840 --> 00:40:47.620 align:middle line:84%
And that's the person
who is balanced,

00:40:47.620 --> 00:40:52.340 align:middle line:84%
who has a beautiful
relationship with themselves.

00:40:52.340 --> 00:40:54.930 align:middle line:84%
So what I'm saying here
is, is your relationship

00:40:54.930 --> 00:40:57.740 align:middle line:84%
with yourself, is your
relationship with life,

00:40:57.740 --> 00:40:59.620 align:middle line:84%
when your relationship
with yourself

00:40:59.620 --> 00:41:03.720 align:middle line:84%
is one of love and appreciation
and respect for yourself,

00:41:03.720 --> 00:41:05.470 align:middle line:90%
you do not cluster.

00:41:05.470 --> 00:41:08.700 align:middle line:84%
And you do not get the
diseases of clustering.

00:41:08.700 --> 00:41:11.930 align:middle line:84%
There's not a hospital on this
planet that has a ward or even

00:41:11.930 --> 00:41:15.930 align:middle line:84%
a room for people to go in and
die who dying from terminal,

00:41:15.930 --> 00:41:17.840 align:middle line:90%
unconditional love.

00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:20.950 align:middle line:84%
Because they don't go
to hospital to die.

00:41:20.950 --> 00:41:22.720 align:middle line:84%
Generally when
you're in that state,

00:41:22.720 --> 00:41:25.950 align:middle line:84%
you can just leave your body
when you feel is appropriate,

00:41:25.950 --> 00:41:28.410 align:middle line:84%
or maybe not quite
appropriate, but you're

00:41:28.410 --> 00:41:32.070 align:middle line:84%
ready to leave it anyway
because there's no attachment.

00:41:32.070 --> 00:41:36.640 align:middle line:84%
And so, I spend a lot of time
traveling metaphysically,

00:41:36.640 --> 00:41:39.110 align:middle line:90%
