00:41:39.110 --> 00:41:41.740 align:middle line:84%
Astral traveling is
when your body's asleep.

00:41:41.740 --> 00:41:43.050 align:middle line:90%
My body's wide awake.

00:41:43.050 --> 00:41:45.570 align:middle line:84%
