through a park.

00:41:45.570 --> 00:41:47.390 align:middle line:84%
And then I like to
move into trees.

00:41:47.390 --> 00:41:48.820 align:middle line:90%
So I'm walking along.

00:41:48.820 --> 00:41:50.220 align:middle line:84%
I generally come
to a standstill,

00:41:50.220 --> 00:41:52.515 align:middle line:84%
