00:41:56.575 --> 00:41:58.740 align:middle line:90%
And I sort of forgot.

00:41:58.740 --> 00:42:00.820 align:middle line:84%
And so you can walk
into a tree and you can

00:42:00.820 --> 00:42:03.160 align:middle line:90%
flow up the tree, up the trunk.

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:04.760 align:middle line:84%
You can flow through
the branches.

00:42:04.760 --> 00:42:08.110 align:middle line:84%
You can flow out
into every leaf.

00:42:08.110 --> 00:42:12.380 align:middle line:84%
And you could feel the
sun on yourself as a leaf.

00:42:12.380 --> 00:42:13.990 align:middle line:84%
And you realize
that no human has

00:42:13.990 --> 00:42:18.380 align:middle line:84%
ever connected with the sun the
way that a leaf on a tree does.

00:42:18.380 --> 00:42:19.680 align:middle line:90%
It feels it.

00:42:19.680 --> 00:42:22.430 align:middle line:90%
It hears it.

00:42:22.430 --> 00:42:23.810 align:middle line:90%
It smells it.

00:42:23.810 --> 00:42:28.860 align:middle line:84%
It knows the sun with
an incredible intimacy.

00:42:28.860 --> 00:42:32.510 align:middle line:84%
It's an amazing
arrange of sounds.

00:42:32.510 --> 00:42:35.530 align:middle line:84%
And inside that leaf, you're
aware of the life forms

00:42:35.530 --> 00:42:39.010 align:middle line:90%
