00:42:39.010 --> 00:42:41.550 align:middle line:84%
And I'll tell you
something else.

00:42:41.550 --> 00:42:46.450 align:middle line:84%
In every leaf, there are nature
spirits, myriads, millions.

00:42:46.450 --> 00:42:50.160 align:middle line:84%
And they take
sunlight as energy,

00:42:50.160 --> 00:42:54.220 align:middle line:84%
as light energy, down
into the branches

00:42:54.220 --> 00:42:56.610 align:middle line:84%
where a different
type of nature spirit

00:42:56.610 --> 00:42:59.640 align:middle line:84%
takes them on down to the
surface of the ground.

00:42:59.640 --> 00:43:02.110 align:middle line:84%
And another one
takes them on down,

00:43:02.110 --> 00:43:04.110 align:middle line:90%
right down to the finest root.

00:43:04.110 --> 00:43:07.595 align:middle line:84%
And right at the tip of every
root , sunlight is there,

00:43:07.595 --> 00:43:09.280 align:middle line:84%
that you couldn't
measure it or see

00:43:09.280 --> 00:43:12.660 align:middle line:84%
it with the human eye or any
of our microscopes or anything.

00:43:12.660 --> 00:43:16.800 align:middle line:84%
But the actual energy of
sun and the light of the sun

00:43:16.800 --> 00:43:22.680 align:middle line:84%
